{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"5":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat): Voluntary Prayers"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1344,"arabicnumber":1344,"text":"حدثنا عثمان بن أبي شيبة، حدثنا محمد بن بشر، حدثنا سعيد، بهذا الحديث قال ‏:‏ يسلم تسليما يسمعنا كما قال يحيى بن سعيد ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":5,"hadith":95}}]}